Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.71,0:00:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,地球形式的求救信号，SOS\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Earth-style distress signal. SOS.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.84,0:00:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我用所有频段回复了一遍，长官，对方无应答\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've answered it on all frequencies, sir. They don't reply.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.76,0:00:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,并非来自星舰，而是来自地面\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Not a vessel, a ground source.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.18,0:00:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,仪器显示信号来自该太阳系第三颗行星\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The third planet in this solar system, according to my instruments.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.18,0:00:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,就在正前方，确定是地球形式的信号\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Directly ahead. Definitely an Earth-style signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.27,0:00:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我们离地球可有数百光年，史波克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We're hundreds of light-years from Earth, Mr. Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.28,0:00:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,此处甚远，既无殖民地也无星舰\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No colonies or vessels out this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.53,0:00:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,行星测量中，舰长，形状为扁圆体\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Measuring the planet now, captain. Spheroid-shaped.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.79,0:00:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,周长24874英里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Circumference, 24,874 miles.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.25,0:00:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,质量，6乘10的21次方吨\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mass, 6 times 10-to-the-21 st-power tons.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.63,0:00:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,平均密度，5.517\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mean density, 5.517.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.13,0:00:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,大气成分…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Atmosphere...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.47,0:00:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,氧气，氮气\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...oxygen-nitrogen.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.64,0:00:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,地球\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.93,0:01:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,不是那个地球，而是另一个\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Not the Earth. Another Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.35,0:01:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,另一个“地球”\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Another Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.49,0:01:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,宇宙，最后的边疆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Space, the final frontier.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.66,0:01:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,这是星舰进取号的航程\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}These are the voyages Of the starship Enterprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.37,0:01:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,它的五年任务，是去探索未知的新世界\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Its five-year mission: To explore strange new worlds,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.46,0:01:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,找寻新的生命与新的文明\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to seek out new life and new civilizations,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.34,0:01:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,勇敢地航向前人未至之境\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to boldly go where no man has gone before.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.28,0:01:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,【星际迷航：原初】
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.63,0:01:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00FFFF&}荣誉出品\N本字幕仅供学习交流，严禁用于商业途径{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.88,0:02:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00FFFF&}-=TLF字幕组=-\N翻译：kmdangdangli 土豆爱 Claire叶子\N校对：心痕依 Micezhang xjCGI{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.69,0:02:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,第一季第八集 米莉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.64,0:02:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长日志，星历2713.5\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain's log, stardate 2713.5:
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.15,0:02:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,距离我们的星系很遥远的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}In the distant reaches of our galaxy,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.98,0:02:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我们有个惊人的发现\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}we have made an astonishing discovery:
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.99,0:02:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,一颗行星发出地球形式的无线电信号\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Earth-type radio signals coming from a planet
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.90,0:02:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,这颗行星简直就是地球的翻版\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}which apparently is an exact duplicate of the Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.99,0:02:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,看似不可能，但它就在眼前\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It seems impossible, but there it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.49,0:02:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,- 固定环绕轨道，史波克 - 是，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Hold us in a fixed orbit, Mr. Spock. - Affirmative, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.04,0:02:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,- 还是没有对方的回复？ - 没有，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Still no response, communications? - None, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.92,0:02:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,传送我们下去，让安全人员待命\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We'll beam down. Alert security.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.71,0:02:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,准备传送外遣队到地面\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Prepare to transport landing party to surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.59,0:02:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我们将在求救信号源附近登陆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We'll land in the vicinity of the distress signal now being received.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.54,0:03:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,一模一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Identical.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.46,0:03:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,20世纪早期的地球就是这样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Earth, as it was in the early 1900s.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.21,0:03:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,更像是中期，舰长，大约1960年\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}More the mid-1900s, I would say, captain, approximately 1960.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.72,0:03:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,但人都跑哪儿去啦？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But where is everybody?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.64,0:03:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,仪器显示，这里发生过自然劣化\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Readings indicate that natural deterioration has been taking place
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.98,0:03:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,至少持续了好几个世纪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}on this planet for at least several centuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.23,0:03:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,- 那就是说人都死啦？ - 还不好说，文书\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- You mean there's no one alive? - Not conclusive, yeoman.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.07,0:03:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,看来求救信号是自动发出的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The evidence would suggest that the distress signal is automated.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.57,0:03:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不可思议\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You know, this is marvellous.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.62,0:03:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我见过最老最破的建筑群\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The most horrible conglomeration of antique architecture I’ve ever seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.72,0:04:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.04,0:04:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我的！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.62,0:04:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,是我的！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.38,0:04:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我的！这是我的！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's mine! It’s mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.30,0:04:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我的！我的！是我的！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mine! Mine! It’s mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.45,0:05:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,它坏了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's broke.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.45,0:05:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,有人把它弄坏了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Somebody broke it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.67,0:05:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,修理\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Fix.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.33,0:05:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,能修好它吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Somebody, please fix.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.13,0:05:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,它肯定还能修好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Of course somebody will fix it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.51,0:05:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然相貌扭曲，可的确近似人类\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Definitely humanoid, in spite of the distortion.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.51,0:05:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,可心智却和小孩一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But with the mind of a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.64,0:05:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,- 老骨头，怎么回事？ - 某种癫痫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Bones, what is it? - A seizure of some type.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.20,0:05:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我们会帮你的 - 撒谎！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- We wanna help you. - Liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.62,0:05:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,骗子，骗子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Fibber, fibber.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.37,0:05:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,骗子，骗子！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Fibber, fibber!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.29,0:06:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,骗子！骗子！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Fibber! Fibber! Fibber! Fibber!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.12,0:06:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,骗子！骗子！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Fibber! Fibber!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.43,0:06:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,它死了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.27,0:06:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不敢相信 - 什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- It's incredible. - What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.35,0:06:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,它新陈代谢的速度\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Its metabolic rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.73,0:06:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,快得无法想象，就像自燃\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's impossibly high, as if it's burning itself up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.65,0:06:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,就刚才那几分钟，他老了一个世纪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Almost as if it aged a century in just the past few minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.24,0:06:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我来！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.41,0:07:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这是什么时候的东西？ - 大概300年前的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- How old is this thing? - About 300 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.26,0:07:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,出来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.47,0:07:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我们并无恶意\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We mean you no harm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.02,0:07:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,别伤害我，求你了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Don't hurt me, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.65,0:07:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm not gonna hurt you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.90,0:07:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,别过来，求你了，我什么都没做\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No, please, don't. I didn't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.90,0:07:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我不会伤害你的 - 别过来，求你了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- I won't hurt you. - No, please, don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.99,0:07:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我只想和你谈谈 - 不，不要，不要伤…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- I only wanna talk to you. - No, don't, don't hurt--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.24,0:08:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,- 出来吧 - 不，不要，求求你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Come on. - No. Don't, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.37,0:08:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我不会伤害你，来吧 - 别伤害我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- I won't hurt you. Come on. - Don't hurt me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.29,0:08:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不要… - 没关系\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Don't-- - It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.83,0:08:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不… - 来这边\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- No-- - Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.00,0:08:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不会伤害你，亲爱的，我们是朋友，别怕\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We won't hurt you, sweetheart. We're your friends. No.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.84,0:08:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,带警卫到外面搜查一下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Take the guards, have a look outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.46,0:08:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,看是否有放射性物质，化学污染，或是其他生命迹象\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Radioactive readings, chemical pollutions, any further sign of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.30,0:08:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,是，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Right, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.18,0:08:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,她经历了什么事？怎么这么怕我们？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I wonder what happened to her that she should be so terrified of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.97,0:09:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,可我还记得你们这些“大大”做的事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But I remember the things you "grups" did.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.56,0:09:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,烧东西，大喊大叫，伤害别人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Burning and yelling, hurting people.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.85,0:09:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,这种事我们从未做过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We didn't do anything like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.11,0:09:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,现在也不会吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're not going to hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.19,0:09:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,不会，当然不会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No, of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.57,0:09:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是来帮忙的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We're here to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.20,0:09:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,“大大”从不会帮忙\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Grups don't help.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.37,0:09:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,但我们会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But we will.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.24,0:09:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,这儿发生了什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What happened here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.20,0:09:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,人都哪去了？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Where is everybody?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.25,0:09:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.46,0:09:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No, I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.38,0:09:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你能告诉我吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Won't you tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.80,0:09:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你想玩“胡闹”吗？你想跟我玩，可我不会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You got a "foolie," is that it? And you want me to play, but I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.88,0:09:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道规则，我得知道规则\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't know the rules. I've got to know the rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.47,0:09:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,- “胡闹”？ - 一种游戏，你知道的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Foolie? - A game, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.27,0:09:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,玩游戏就得知道游戏规则\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You can't play a game without rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.94,0:09:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,即使“大大”也得知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Even grups ought to know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.60,0:09:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,- 谁是“大大”？ - 你们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- What are grups? - You are.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.36,0:09:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,“恩里斯”长大了就是“大大”【恩里斯指这里的小孩】\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They were when "onlies" get old.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.03,0:10:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,成年人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Grown-ups.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.95,0:10:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你刚才说这些“大大”做坏事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You said something about the grups doing bad things.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.33,0:10:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,大喊大叫，打人，烧东西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yelling, hurting, burning.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.13,0:10:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,他们生病的时候就变这样了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That was when they started to get sick in the before time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.50,0:10:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我们躲了起来然后他们就不见了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We hid, then they were gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.59,0:10:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我这样做对吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Am I doing all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.93,0:10:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你做的很好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're doing fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.93,0:10:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你说“大大”们都生病了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You said the grups got sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.93,0:10:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是因为这样他们才不见了？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Is that why there aren't any of them around?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.64,0:10:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,是，他们都死了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes. They died.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.06,0:10:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,但是在做了这些可怕的事情后\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But that was after the awful things.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.78,0:10:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,是瘟疫，舰长，只有瘟疫才会这样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A plague, captain. That could explain a lot of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.57,0:10:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子们呢？就是这的“恩里斯”\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But what about the children, the onlies?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.95,0:10:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,可怕的事情有没有影响到他们？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Didn't the awful things affect them?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.95,0:10:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,当然没有，我们不是还活着吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Of course not. We're here, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.16,0:10:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,- 除你以外还有多少？ - 都活着\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- More of you? How many? - All there are.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.02,0:11:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你叫什么名字？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.31,0:11:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,米莉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Miri.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.78,0:11:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,名字真好听…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Pretty name...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.03,0:11:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,人也很漂亮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...for a pretty young woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.37,0:11:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,漂亮？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Pretty?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.37,0:11:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,非常漂亮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Very pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.62,0:12:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,警卫！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Guards!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.71,0:12:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,掩护我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Cover me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.31,0:13:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子，舰长，有很多孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Children, captain. Lots of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.86,0:13:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,无法接近他们，一走近，他们便一哄而散\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We couldn't begin to get close to them. They just seemed to scurry away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.78,0:13:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,- 像动物似的，只有孩子 - 米莉说所有大人都死了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Like animals, only children. - Miri said all the adults died.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.11,0:13:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,攻击我们的那个家伙绝对不是小孩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That creature which attacked us was certainly no child.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.08,0:13:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,导致它死亡的原因也许就是女孩说的那种病\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Perhaps it died of the disease the girl's talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.25,0:13:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,这里肯定有记录可寻\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There must be records somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.75,0:13:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,可以解开我们的疑问\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And answers to some of our questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.17,0:13:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,米莉？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Miri?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.42,0:13:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道医生以前都在哪工作吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Do you know any buildings where the doctors used to work?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.68,0:13:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,知道，我还知道他们的药品在哪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes, I know that. Them and their pills and things.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.01,0:13:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,- 能带我去吗？ - 那里好恐怖\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Will you take me there? - That's a bad place.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.77,0:14:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,这很重要\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's important.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.44,0:14:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,- 算我求你 - 好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Please. - All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.53,0:14:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你也有名字吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Do you have a name too?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.82,0:14:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- 有，我叫吉姆 - 这名字我喜欢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Yes. It's Jim. - I like that name.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.95,0:14:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,那就好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.58,0:14:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我也喜欢你的名字\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I like yours too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.87,0:14:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,人也很喜欢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.83,0:14:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,真的？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Do you really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.04,0:14:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会骗你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I wouldn't lie to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.05,0:14:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不会骗你，吉姆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I wouldn't lie to you either, Jim.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.93,0:14:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我记得这的大大，你不一样，你是好人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I remember the grups, but you're nice. You're different.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.43,0:14:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,多谢夸奖\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Why, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.07,0:14:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,开始了，我就知道会这样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's already starting. I knew it would.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.94,0:14:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,就像这里的大大一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Just like it did with the grups.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.20,0:14:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,它会蔓延到你全身，你会大叫，会伤害所有人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It'll spread all over you. You'll yell, you'll try to hurt everybody,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.07,0:14:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,最后你会死，我就知道会这样，我就知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and then you'll die. I knew it would, I knew it would.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.69,0:15:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长日志，星历2713.6\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain's log, stardate 2713.6:
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.07,0:15:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,米莉带我们去的那栋楼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The building Miri led us to also housed
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.87,0:15:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,还有一座自动传输站\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}an automatic transmission station,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.70,0:15:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,就是那的信号，把我们引到这里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}which sent out the signals that drew us to this planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.58,0:15:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我们还发现\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}we also discovered something else:
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.79,0:15:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,所有人都得了一种莫名的疾病\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That the blue splotches characteristic of the unknown disease
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.42,0:15:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,身上都出现了蓝斑，除了史波克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}had appeared on each of us, with the exception of Mr. spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.88,0:15:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,这栋楼有间化验室，设备齐全\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There was a well-equipped laboratory in the building.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.18,0:15:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,麦考伊医生采集了每个人身上的组织细胞\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Dr. McCoy took tissue samples of each of us
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.55,0:15:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,试图分离出病毒组织\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}in an attempt to isolate the organism responsible.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.35,0:15:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,真是名副其实的细菌动物园\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A veritable zoo of bacteria.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.40,0:15:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,传送一台生物电脑和一台便携式电子显微镜\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Beam down a bio-computer and a portable electronic microscope.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.03,0:15:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我在和病毒打交道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}lf I'm gonna be dealing with viruses,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.74,0:15:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,需要更好的仪器\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm gonna need better equipment than I have here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.41,0:16:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好的，医生，寇克舰长？ - 什么事，上尉？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Yes, doctor. Captain Kirk? - Yes, lieutenant?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.53,0:16:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我们有人想自愿下来帮忙，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've got volunteers standing by ready to help you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.49,0:16:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不管发生什么，任何人都不许离开星舰\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Under no circumstances do I want anyone to beam down from the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.33,0:16:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,必须防止病菌进一步蔓延\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We can't take any chances with further contamination.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.58,0:16:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,- 可舰长，要是你病情加重… - 我的命令依然有效，上尉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- But, captain, if you become too ill-- - My orders still stand, lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.29,0:16:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你们可以帮我整理电脑资料库并待命，通话完毕\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You can help by clearing the computer banks and standing by. Kirk out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.93,0:16:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,老骨头\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Bones.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.76,0:16:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么史波克身上没有这种病症？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Why do you think the symptoms haven't appeared on Mr. Spock?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.27,0:16:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.77,0:16:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,也许这些小病菌或微生物什么的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Probably the little bugs, or whatever they are,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.77,0:16:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,觉得绿色的血液味道不好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}have no appetite for green blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.53,0:16:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,看来红色的血液显然会成为人类的缺点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Being a red-blooded human obviously has its disadvantages.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.95,0:16:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,瞧桌上这玩意儿可以当文物了，大夫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now, there you have a museum piece, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.33,0:16:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,透镜型，手动操作，光感的…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Lens-type, manually operated, light-activated--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.29,0:16:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,就不能消停一下吗，史波克？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Spare me the analysis, Mr. Spock, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.29,0:16:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,能用就不错了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's enough that it works.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.18,0:17:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,扩散的好快，我就知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It spreads real fast, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.64,0:17:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,只要变成大大，它就会遍布全身\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}When you're old, it covers you like anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.44,0:17:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,“就生命延长实验项目的…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}"Intermediate experimentation report project on life...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.95,0:17:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,中期报告”\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...prolongation."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.58,0:17:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,“进度报告，遗传部门，生命延长项目”\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}"Progress report, genetics section. Life prolongation project."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.29,0:17:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,原来如此\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So that's what it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.63,0:17:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,生命延长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Life prolongation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.01,0:17:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,进展得不太走运吧？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Didn't have much luck, did they?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.73,0:17:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长日志\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain's log:
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.19,0:17:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,麦考伊医生的生物电脑及便携式电子显微镜\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Dr. McCoy's bio-computer and a portable electronic microscope
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.03,0:17:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,已从进取号传送下来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}have been beamed down from the Enterprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.32,0:17:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,它们将会和船上的电脑资料库相连\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They will be used in conjunction with computer banks onboard ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.91,0:18:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,管状物，极具多样性\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Tubular, with extreme multiplicability.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.16,0:18:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,类似核酸，把查到的信息告诉我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Appear to have affinity for nucleic acids. Give me what you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.84,0:18:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,- 三百年前的事，舰长 - 所有的成年人都死了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- This was 300 years ago, captain. - All the adults are dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.38,0:18:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,只有孩子们活下来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Only the children are left alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.18,0:18:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,但孩子们会长大成人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But children become adults.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.18,0:18:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,至少目前为止他们还活着\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}At least they have up to now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.90,0:18:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,医生…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.53,0:18:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,在进入青春期时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...there are certain glandular changes which take place
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.99,0:18:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,有些腺体会发生变化，对吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}upon entering puberty, are there not?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.12,0:18:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,当然，改变了整个身体系统\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Of course. It changes the entire body system.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.66,0:18:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.04,0:18:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,当然知道，怎么了？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Of course you know that. Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.50,0:18:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,这里的孩子们会不会是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Is it not possible that these children here,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.34,0:18:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,由于进入青春期，而感染的疾病呢？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}as they enter puberty, contract the disease?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.55,0:19:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,那就能解释为什么没有成年人了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That would explain why there are no adults.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.97,0:19:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,腺体，青春期后期，可能是这样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Glandular, post-pubescent. It could be.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.31,0:19:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,还是不合逻辑，不能理解的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's illogical. It does not follow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.94,0:19:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,这颗行星上所有的成年人都在300年前死了…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All the adults on this planet died 300 years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.78,0:19:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,…但现在大街上还有孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...but there are children in the streets.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.32,0:19:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,他们进入青春期就会死去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Who die when they enter adolescence.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.25,0:19:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,但是他们的生命怎么延续的呢？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But how do they keep their line going?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.75,0:19:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,还有一件事，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}One thing, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.71,0:19:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,如果她自从小女孩起就像野兽一样没人管\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If she were a wild animal ever since she's been a little girl,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.59,0:19:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你如何解释她愿意和我们呆在一起？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}how do you explain that she wants to stay with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.22,0:19:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,孤独？我不知道，好奇？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Loneliness? I don't know. Curiosity?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.84,0:19:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我想孩子们天生就需要成年人陪伴\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I think children have an instinctive need for adults.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.60,0:19:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,他们想被告知对错与否\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They want to be told right and wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.06,0:19:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,这种情况中可能还有其他感情因素，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There may be other emotions at work in this case, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.44,0:19:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,她喜欢你，吉姆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}She likes you, Jim.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.69,0:19:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,她正在成长为一个女人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}She's becoming a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.29,0:20:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.96,0:20:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我是史波克 - 下面是您要的数据\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Spock here. - Here are those figures you asked for.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.30,0:20:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,12的10次方\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Twelve to the tenth power.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.34,0:20:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,代谢率，72%\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Metabolic rate, 72 percent.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.85,0:20:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,核酸量降至正常水平的33%\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Production of nucleic acids reduced to 33 percent of normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.48,0:20:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,惯用时序级数，3.6分之100\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Conventional chronological progression, 100 by 3.6.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.49,0:20:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,收到，上尉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Acknowledged, lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.99,0:20:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在知道他们的算法了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I have their calculations now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.41,0:20:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,再试试，看看能不能在其他方面发现点什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Try again. See if you can find anything outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.00,0:20:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.00,0:20:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,帮我擦擦那张桌子，好吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Clean up that desk for me, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.05,0:21:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好啊，吉姆 - 谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- All right, Jim. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.01,0:21:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,按照他们的生命延续计划\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}According to their life prolongation plan,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.81,0:21:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,他们认为正在实现的算法是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}what they thought they were accomplishing,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.72,0:21:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,在实际时间的每100年内，一个人只长大一个月\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}a person would age only one month for every 100 years of real time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.19,0:21:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,100年，仅长大一个月？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}One hundred years, and only one month?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.36,0:21:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,没错，文书\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Exactly, yeoman.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.53,0:21:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,显而易见，由于某处有误算\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Evidently, through some miscalculation,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.57,0:21:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,导致这种病毒在很短的时间段内\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}this virus annihilated the entire adult population
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.58,0:21:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,摧毁了整个成年人群，只留下了孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}in a very short period, leaving only the children.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.20,0:21:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,但那就意味着这些孩子…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But that means these children...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.41,0:21:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,应该已经非常老了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Could very well be immensely old.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.92,0:21:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,那就回答了这个问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That would certainly answer the question
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.71,0:21:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,他们的父母当年发生了什么事情\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}of what happened to their parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.46,0:21:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,- 很好的答案 - 孩子们永远长不大\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Answers it very well. - Children who never age.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.51,0:21:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,永远的儿童时代，可以尽情玩耍，没有责任\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Eternal childhood filled with play, no responsibilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.68,0:21:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,简直像一场梦\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's almost like a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.01,0:21:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会太靠近这个梦的，文书\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I wouldn't examine that dream too closely, yeoman.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.06,0:21:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,可能结果并不是很美好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It might not turn out to be very pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.23,0:22:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,几天前，或者一个星期前，那个袭击我们的生物\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A few days ago, or a week ago, that creature that attacked us
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.65,0:22:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,可能一直和米莉一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}could have been just like Miri.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.57,0:22:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,在这颗行星上的孩子进入青春期\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A child entering puberty on this planet
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.91,0:22:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,就意味着死刑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}means a death sentence.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.91,0:22:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你认为她知道吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Do you suppose she knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.33,0:22:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为她不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.75,0:22:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,哦，如果他们像史波克说的那么老\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, if they're as old as Spock claims,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.54,0:22:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,他们一定了解一些当年的情况\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}they must have some idea of what's happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.92,0:22:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,对这里没有成年人能做些解释\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There's no adult interpretation.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.05,0:22:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为我们得和这些孩子打交道，他们可能很老了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I think we're dealing with children. Immensely old, perhaps,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.14,0:22:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,但毕竟他们还是孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but nonetheless children.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.14,0:22:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我得从其他人身上下手\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've gotta do something about the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.93,0:22:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,那很难，如果我们都见不到他们的话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Difficult, if we can't even get a glimpse of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.77,0:22:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能接近其他的孩子吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You couldn't get close to the other kids?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.06,0:22:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,不可能，他们很了解这个地区\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Impossible. They know the area too well.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.81,0:22:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,就像老鼠\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Like mice.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.40,0:22:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我要试一试\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm gonna try.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.86,0:22:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,米莉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Miri.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.74,0:22:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,过来一下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.63,0:23:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你想和我一起转转吗？ - 当然\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- You wanna go someplace with me? - Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.93,0:23:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,那个小女孩…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That little girl--
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.56,0:23:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,比你至少年长300岁，文书\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Is at least 300 years older than you are, yeoman.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.48,0:23:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,想一想吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.51,0:23:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,米莉跟他们在一起，为什么？为什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Miri is with them. Why? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.10,0:23:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你打算怎么办，雅恩？ - 我不…我不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- What you gonna do, Jahn? - I don't-- I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.52,0:24:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道我们怎么办了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I know what we've gotta do.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.65,0:24:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,他们比我们看到的人要多，在某个地方\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There's more of them than we see. Somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.86,0:24:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,可能在天上，某个地方\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Up in the sky, maybe. Somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.57,0:24:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,他们一直互相交谈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They talk to each other all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.20,0:24:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你们知道大大吧，你们知道大大都干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You know grups. You know what they do.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.37,0:24:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,伤害、杀戮…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The hurting, the killing...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.75,0:24:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我记得，雅恩，那是以前… - 没错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- I remember, Jahn, the way it was-- - That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.00,0:24:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,就和以前一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The way it was in the before time.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.71,0:24:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,他们用小盒子与其他的大大说话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They talk to the other grups with these little boxes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.89,0:24:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,既然如此，如果他们没有了那些小盒子…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now, if they didn't have those little boxes...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.89,0:24:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,…他们就孤立了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...they'd be all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.98,0:24:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,但是他们看不见我们，我们藏起来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But they don't see us. We hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.11,0:24:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,- 找啊，找啊，找不到我 - 找啊，找啊，找不到我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Ollie, ollie, oxen free - Ollie, ollie, oxen free
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.82,0:24:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,- 找啊，找啊，找不到我 - 不！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Ollie, ollie, oxen free - No!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.08,0:24:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是游戏\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's not a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.04,0:25:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,这是实战\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's real.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.33,0:25:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,他们很危险，他们是大大，你们不明白吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They're dangerous. They're grups. Don't you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.46,0:25:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,雅恩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Jahn.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.93,0:25:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧，咱们藏起来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All right, let's hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.08,0:26:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,死了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.29,0:26:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我不太明白，我的相位枪没有设定成致死状态啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't understand it. My phaser wasn't set to kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.17,0:26:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,她叫路易丝\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Her name was Louise.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.47,0:26:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,事情发生时她只是比我年长一些\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}She was a little bit older than I am when it happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.47,0:26:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,噢，吉姆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, Jim.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.28,0:26:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,数据已经输入计算机，史波克先生，候命中\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Data has been fed into the computers, Mr. Spock. stand by.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.49,0:26:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,收到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Acknowledged.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.82,0:27:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,这些够了吗，吉姆？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Are these enough, Jim?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.53,0:27:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你不介意的话，我们可能用的再多些\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We could use some more, if you don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.45,0:27:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不，我不介意\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No, I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.96,0:27:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你在这找到的不应该有问题啊？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There couldn't be any doubt about what you've found here?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.59,0:27:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,在发病后，这家伙在死前的几个星期作了记录\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This fellow made these notes in the last weeks, after the disaster began.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.56,0:27:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我先不管这些后面的记录，他说他自己病得严重\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I disregard these last entries. He said himself he was too sick,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.86,0:27:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,没法确定他还没有疯，我同意\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}too far gone to be sure he wasn't already mad, and I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.03,0:27:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,但是按照前面的记录\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But based on the entries he made before that,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.28,0:27:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道我们还剩多少时间\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I know how much time we have.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.12,0:27:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,船上的电脑会验证我的数据\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The ship's computers will verify my figures.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.58,0:27:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,只是时间问题，我们全都会变疯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Only a matter of time before we all go mad,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.21,0:27:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,互相残杀，直到最后的那个人自己毁掉自己\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}destroy each other, till the last of us finally destroys himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.52,0:28:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,米莉呢？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What about Miri?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.02,0:28:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的猜测是对的，他们进入青春期就会染上疾病\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Our guess was correct. They contract the disease as they enter puberty
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.94,0:28:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,他们的新陈代谢有了变化，笔记还提示了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and their metabolism changes. The notes would indicate
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.73,0:28:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不太精确的时间，也就1个月左右\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that it doesn't become acute for a month or so.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.61,0:28:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我估计她可能还剩5、6个星期\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I estimate she has perhaps five or six weeks left.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.37,0:28:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我们呢？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What about us?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.62,0:28:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,受害者越年长，疾病的发展速度越快\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The older the victim, the more rapid the progress of the disease.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.33,0:28:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,那你呢？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And you?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.17,0:28:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,好像疾病对你不感兴趣\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The disease doesn't seem to be interested in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.25,0:28:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我是携带者，无论怎样，我也不能回星舰了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I am a carrier. Whatever happens, I can't go back to the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.47,0:28:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,可我确实想回星舰，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And I do want to go back to the ship, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.01,0:28:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,当然，史波克先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Of course, Mr. Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.94,0:28:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我们还是不知道我们要对抗的是什么吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We still don't know what we're fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.48,0:28:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊，但我们知道了诱因，致命有多迅速\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No, but we know what it is, and how fast it does it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.40,0:29:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,它的进程，我们很快就会从五脏六腑感受到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's progressing. We'll begin to feel it inside soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.82,0:29:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,高烧，手脚剧烈疼痛\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Intense fever, great pain in the extremities,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.78,0:29:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,视觉模糊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}fuzziness of vision.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.16,0:29:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,当然，那些只是早期症状，后面症状会越来越多\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Of course, those are the early symptoms. There'll be more.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.04,0:29:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你确定我们剩下的时间吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Are you certain about the time we have left?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.96,0:29:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为我的计算准确无误\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I presume my calculations are correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.34,0:29:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- 有没有可能…？ - 外遣队，这里是进取号\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Is there any possibility--? - Landing party, this is the Enterprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.97,0:29:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我是史波克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Spock here.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.13,0:29:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,计算机显示还有170小时，史波克先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Computer indicates 170 hours, Mr. Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.05,0:29:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,确认了，舰长，我们还有7天时间\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Verified, captain. We have seven days.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.06,0:29:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长日志，补充\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain's log, supplement:
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.40,0:29:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,今天是我们剩余7天中的第2天，还没有什么发现\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It is the second day of the seven left to us. We've found nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.44,0:29:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,进取号全体实验室、计算机都待命中，准备实施援助\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Enterprise is standing by with its labs, computers, ready to assist us,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.74,0:29:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,但是没有数据，无从下手\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but there is no data, no starting point.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.37,0:29:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我想我找到了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I think I've found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.91,0:30:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- 贾尼丝，带米莉走走 - 是，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Janice, take Miri for a walk. - Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.59,0:30:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,只有一半的完整性\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Only one half intact.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.09,0:30:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,但你知道他们当时要做什么了？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But do you know what they were up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.92,0:30:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,差不多吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}More or less.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.55,0:30:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,他们的办法是造出新系列的疾病\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The idea was to create a new series of diseases,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.64,0:30:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,其病毒的反应链意味着生命的延续\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}a chain reaction of viruses meant essentially to extend the life
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.14,0:30:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,让人类细胞无限制成长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}of the human cell immeasurably.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.10,0:30:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,不幸的是，他们没有成功，我们已经看到了结果\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Unfortunately, they weren't successful. We've seen the results.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.69,0:30:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你们两人必须再现他们的想法，如果能分离出病毒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You two will have to recreate their thinking. lf you can isolate that virus,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.11,0:30:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你们就能制造疫苗了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}you'll be able to develop a vaccine.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.28,0:30:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,就这样，舰长？我们还有5天，你知道的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Is that all, captain? We have five days, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.46,0:30:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.17,0:30:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Children.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.95,0:31:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,- 发现什么了？你呢？ - 没有，什么也没发现\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Anything? You? - No. Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.31,0:31:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,是通讯器，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The communicators, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.94,0:31:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,通讯器不见了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They're gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.19,0:31:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,吉姆，我们绝对要用到通讯器\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Jim, we've absolutely gotta have those communicators.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.44,0:31:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,没有通讯器，我们就没有了计算机\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Without them, we don't have the computers.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.24,0:31:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,没有计算机，我们就没有一丝机会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And without the computers, we don't have a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.50,0:32:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长日志，星历2717.3\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain's log, stardate 2717.3:
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.42,0:32:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我们还剩3天零7个小时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Three days, seven hours left to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.46,0:32:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,研究表明该地区的食物供给余量\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}lnvestigation proves that the supply of food left in the area
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.51,0:32:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,极度不足，除非做点什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}is running dangerously low. Unless something is done,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.26,0:32:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,否则孩子们将在几个月后挨饿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the children will staeve in a few months.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.55,0:32:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,另外，疾病也影响了我们每一个人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}In addition, the disease is working on each of us
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.85,0:32:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,按照麦考伊医生的预言，我们的脾气越来越差\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}according to Dr. McCoy's prediction. Our tempers are growing short,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.81,0:32:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不像2天前那么融洽\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and we are no further along than we were two days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.52,0:32:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你还没什么发现吗？ - 你想尝试一下吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Haven't you found a thing yet? - Would you like to take a crack at it?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.87,0:32:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,不！不！不！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No! No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.96,0:32:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,不！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.44,0:33:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我很烦，舰长，非常烦\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm upset, captain. So upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.53,0:33:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,在星舰上的时候，我一直努力想让你看我的腿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Back on the ship, I used to try to get you to look at my legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.96,0:33:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.13,0:33:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,…看看我的腿吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...look at my legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.82,0:34:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都很害怕\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We're all frightened.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.00,0:34:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,吉姆，我有发现了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Jim, I found something.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.38,0:34:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,实验的最后一个载片，我没有调节好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The last slide I examined, I failed to make the necessary adjustment
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.47,0:34:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,- 没有让它慢下来… - 无所谓，你发现什么了？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- for the slowing down-- - Never mind. What did you find?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.93,0:34:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,疾病，舰长，300年前他们创造的疾病\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The disease, captain. The one they created 300 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.18,0:34:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,- 有机会了！ - 有机会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- There's a chance! - A chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.69,0:34:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,至少现在赛跑开始了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}At least it's a race now.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.10,0:34:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,而我们刚浪费了一分钟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And we've just wasted a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.96,0:34:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我承认那会有些乐子，米莉，但能行吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'll admit it would be some foolie, Miri, but do you think it'd work?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.71,0:35:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道，我知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I know, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.76,0:35:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你认为我没听到他们谈话吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Don't you think I've heard them talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.97,0:35:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,他们没有多少时间去做他们那蠢事了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They have such little time to do this dumb thing of theirs,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.64,0:35:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,那些狗拿耗子的事了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}this "buttinsky" thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.06,0:35:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们把她引走，那个文书\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And if we get her away, that yeoman,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.10,0:35:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,那就可以少对付一个人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that's one person less to start off with.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.94,0:35:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,但怎么做呢，米莉？如果他们很忙的话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But how, Miri? If they're so busy,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.11,0:35:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他们有紧急大事的话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}if they're gonna have the big emergency,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.02,0:35:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你怎么把她弄走呢？ - 很简单\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- how are you gonna get her away? - It's easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.61,0:35:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,她老是问我最小的恩里斯的事情\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}She's always asking me about the youngest little onlies, the little ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.16,0:35:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,“如果他们生病了怎么办？谁照顾他们？”\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}"What if they get sick? Who takes care of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.58,0:35:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,“他们吃的够吗？他们在哪里睡觉呢？”\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Do they have enough to eat? Where do they sleep?"
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.75,0:35:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我只要告诉她你们当中的一个受伤倒下了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'll just tell her one of you fell down and got hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.71,0:35:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,- 说我，说是我 - 好的，就说是你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Me, say it's me. - All right, you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.38,0:35:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,但大大什么事情都知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But grups, they know things and all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.96,0:35:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,就算他们少了一个人也能照旧想办法\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You know, I bet they'll be able to do it with one person less.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.22,0:35:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,不是一个人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Not one.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.47,0:35:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,两个\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Two.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.93,0:35:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,因为他会去找她\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Because he'll try to find her.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.85,0:35:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,谁啊，谁会去找她，米莉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Who? Who will, Miri?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.77,0:35:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.19,0:36:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,他会去找她，但他一定找不到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He'll try to find her, but he won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.19,0:36:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,- 多情的先生 - 多情\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Mr. Lovey-dovey. - Lovey-dovey.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.28,0:36:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,敲，敲，敲死他，敲死他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Bonk, bonk on the head. Bonk, bonk! Bonk, bonk!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.62,0:36:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,敲死他，敲死他，敲死他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Bonk, bonk! Bonk, bonk! Bonk, bonk!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.87,0:36:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,敲死他，敲死他，敲死他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Bonk, bonk! Bonk, bonk! Bonk, bonk! Bonk, bonk!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.67,0:36:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- 看上去是了 - 氮化合物循环，应该是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- It looks right. - The nitrogen cycle? It has to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.09,0:36:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,是，可问题是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yeah, but the question is:
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.05,0:36:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,要用多少的量呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What's the dosage?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.85,0:36:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,这真是个好问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That is a very good question.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.31,0:36:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,米莉，她去哪里了？贾尼丝去哪里了？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Where is she, Miri? Where is she, Miri? Where is Janice?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.85,0:36:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你干什么啊？我怎么知道？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What's the matter with you? How should I know?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.36,0:36:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,她去哪儿了？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.65,0:36:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,- 她出什么事了？ - 你还好吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Has something happened to her? - Don't you feel all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.99,0:36:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,不，我不好，我们都不好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No, I don't feel all right! None of us feel all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.53,0:37:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你难道没看到现在的状况吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Can't you see what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.12,0:37:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,吉姆，我不希望你有事啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Jim, I don't want anything to happen to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.80,0:37:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我要去找贾尼丝 - 这还不够，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- I've gotta find Janice. - That's not all, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.09,0:37:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我们还要找到通讯器\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We've got to find those communicators.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.01,0:37:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我们尽力了，史波克，我们已经够尽力了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We're trying, Mr. Spock. We're trying hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.84,0:37:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,这还不够\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's not good enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.68,0:37:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,这可能就是解药了，但我们没有星舰上的电脑就不能测试\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This could be it, but we can't test it without the ship's computers.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.56,0:37:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我们必须找到通讯器，吉姆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We've got to have those communicators, Jim.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.31,0:37:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是那疫苗吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is the vaccine?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.23,0:37:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是只有电脑检测了才知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's what the computers will tell us.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.69,0:37:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,没有电脑，这有可能就是一杯致死的毒药\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Without them, it could be a beaker full of death.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.33,0:37:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你听到了吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Did you hear them?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.50,0:37:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我们只有几个小时的命了 - 这不关我的事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- We only have a few hours left. - I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.59,0:37:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,这当然关你的事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You've got to care.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.89,0:38:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,米莉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Miri.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.85,0:38:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我要告诉你一些事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm gonna tell you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.15,0:38:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.11,0:38:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你的朋友，所有的恩里斯，都会得上这种病的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...your friends, all the onlies, are gonna get the disease
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.65,0:38:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,除非我们研究的疫苗成功了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}unless we succeed in what we're doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.78,0:38:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你也看到了你的一些朋友得上这种病了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You've seen some of your friends get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.49,0:38:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,- 那只是偶尔 - 这不是偶尔，是必然，米莉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Sometimes it happens-- - Not sometimes, all the times, Miri!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.12,0:38:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,只要你一开始长大，你现在就是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}As soon as you start growing up, the way you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.63,0:38:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道你为什么不喜欢玩游戏了吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Don't you know why you don't like to play games anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.80,0:38:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么看你朋友的方式和以前不同了？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Why you don't see your friends the way you used to?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.14,0:38:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,那是因为你已经在长大了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's because you're becoming a young woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.44,0:38:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,而你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.69,0:38:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,在长大的同时，你也在感染上这种病毒，你们都会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...the moment you become a young woman, you get the disease, all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.40,0:38:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的，那只是偶然情况\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's not true. It just happens sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.28,0:38:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,全都是这样的，米莉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All the time, Miri!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.57,0:39:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在已经感染上了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's happening to you right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.32,0:39:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你看看，米莉，病毒已经渗透到你身体里了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Look at it. Look at it, Miri! It's in you!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.62,0:39:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不！ - 你看看！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- No! - Look at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.29,0:39:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.55,0:39:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不对，你玩的不对，我和你说了，当老师\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No, you got the wrong game. A teacher, I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.68,0:39:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,老师会说什么呢，嗯？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now what does a teacher say, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.39,0:39:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,对啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.44,0:39:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,学习，学习！否则敲死你，坏孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Study, study, study! Or bonk, bonk, bad kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.24,0:39:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这一点都不好玩 - 这是“胡闹”游戏\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- It's not funny. - It's a foolie.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.83,0:39:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你们想拿我怎么样？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What are you gonna do with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.37,0:39:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你以为我会告诉你吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You think I'd tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.46,0:39:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,米莉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Miri.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.96,0:40:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你不应该来这里 - 我知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- You're not supposed to be here. - I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.18,0:40:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了，出什么事了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What's the matter? Something go wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.05,0:40:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,- 没事 - 那好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- No. - Okay, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.39,0:40:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,那就别站在门口了，进来吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Just don't stand there in the doorway. Come on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.02,0:40:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,- 听他说 - 你给我听着，米莉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Listen to him. - You listen, Miri!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.90,0:40:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我听了，否则你认为我为什么带他来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I did. Why do you think I brought him here?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.07,0:40:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,- 告诉他们吧，吉姆 - 告诉他们吧，吉姆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Tell them, Jim. - "Tell them, Jim."
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.57,0:40:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉他们吧，吉姆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Tell them, Jim. - Tell them, Jim!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.99,0:40:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉他们吧，吉姆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Tell them, Jim! Tell them, Jim! Tell them, Jim! Tell them, Jim!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.42,0:40:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,- 告诉他们吧，吉姆！ - 大家听我说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Tell them, Jim! Tell them, Jim! - Listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.18,0:40:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,- 听我说！ - 他在课堂上喧哗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Listen to me! - Yelling in the classroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.60,0:40:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,大家看，他是坏学生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Look at him. A very bad citizen.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.43,0:40:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是游戏，这一开始就不是游戏\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This isn't a game. There never was a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.77,0:40:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,- 叫警察叔叔抓他！ - 我就是警察\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Call the police! - I'm the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.98,0:40:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你只要不乖我就敲死你 - 你演的是老师\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Bonk, bonk, unless you're good. - You're the teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.82,0:41:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我两个都是，敲死你，敲死你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I got two jobs! Bonk, bonk!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.02,0:41:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,听我说，你们偷走了我们的通讯器\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Listen to me! You've got our communicators...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.81,0:41:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我们对着说话的那个盒子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...the boxes we talk into.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.94,0:41:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要用它们来和星舰对话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We need them to talk to the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.03,0:41:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,别再吵啦\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No blah, blah, blah!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.07,0:41:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们不能和星舰联络上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Because if we don't talk to the ship...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.45,0:41:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你们不帮助我们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...if you don't help us...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.79,0:41:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,以后就再也没有游戏可以玩了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...there won't be any games anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.38,0:41:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,以后什么都没有了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There won't be anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.05,0:41:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,什么都没有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.88,0:41:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,不会有大大，也不会有恩里斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No grups, no onlies.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.72,0:41:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,最后谁都不会活下来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Nobody left...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.56,0:41:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,永远都不会有了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...forever and ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.23,0:41:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长小心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.99,0:42:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,现在听我说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.95,0:42:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你们一定要帮我们，现在还来得及\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You've got to help us before it's too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.12,0:42:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,放了贾尼丝，趁现在还来得及快把通讯器还给我们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Let Janice go. Give me those communicators before it's too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.31,0:42:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你们也见到你们的朋友一个个长大后都变了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You've seen your friends change one by one as they grew up.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.52,0:42:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你们有见到例外的吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Did you ever see one of them not change?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.94,0:42:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,一个接一个，他们都得上了这种病，都变成了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}One by one, they got the disease, and they became like--
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.19,0:42:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你们害怕的东西，就像路易丝\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Like-- Like those creatures you're afraid of, like Louise.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.70,0:42:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,一个接一个，他们都会变，染上这病毒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}One by one, they changed and got the disease.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.95,0:42:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,就像我得的这种病，像米莉得的这种\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The disease, like I’ve got, like Miri has.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.37,0:42:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你们知道我在说什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You understand what I'm talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.41,0:42:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你们已经不是小孩子了，我们能帮助你们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're not babies. We can help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.16,0:42:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,坏大大，敲死他，敲死他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Naughty grup! Bonk, bonk!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.71,0:43:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,- 敲死他！ - 不，求你们了，不要\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Bonk, bonk! - No! Please! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.18,0:43:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你也会得上的，也就是几个月的事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's waiting for you. Maybe only a matter of months.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.60,0:43:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,听他说，他说的是事实\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Listen to him. He's telling the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.94,0:43:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他真滑稽，他觉得他很滑稽 - 敲死他，敲死他，打死他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- He's funny. He thinks he's funny. - Bonk, bonk! Hit him!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.23,0:43:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,看看我的手臂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Look at my arms!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.82,0:43:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,这也会发生在你们身上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's what's gonna happen to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.74,0:43:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,- 除非让我帮你们 - 敲死他，敲死他，打他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- ...unless you let me help you. - Bonk, bonk! Hit him!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.33,0:43:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,- 敲死他，敲死他！ - 那些最小的孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Bonk, bonk! - And the little ones...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.83,0:43:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你们死后他们怎么办…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What's gonna happen to them after you've gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.75,0:43:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你们变成路易丝那样，他们还在这\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...after you've turned into creatures like Louise? Oh, they'll still be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.55,0:43:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,但他们也不会活太久，因为食物不够了，你们吃完了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But not for long, because the food's all gone. You've eaten it.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.63,0:43:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,估计只能吃上六个月了，就只有这些了，没东西可吃了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Maybe six months left. That's all. And then nothing left to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.02,0:43:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,没人能照顾他们了，他们也会死的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Nobody left to take care of them. They'll die too.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.77,0:44:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,看看我的手臂，我已经得上这病了，他是说实话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Look at my arm, Jahn. It’s happening to me. He's telling the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.73,0:44:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他们是大大！ - 敲死他，敲死他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- They're grups! - Bonk, bonk!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.69,0:44:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,敲死他，敲死他，敲死他，敲死他！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Bonk, bonk! Bonk, bonk! Bonk, bonk! Bonk, bonk!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.91,0:44:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,- 敲死他，敲死他！ - 好吧，你们想玩是吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Bonk, bonk! - All right, you want a foolie?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.99,0:44:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我谅你不敢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All right. I dare you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.16,0:44:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你绝对不敢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I double dare you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.88,0:44:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,看看我脸上的血，再看看你们的手\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Look at the blood on my face. Now look at your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.17,0:44:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你们手上的血\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Blood on your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.30,0:44:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我是谁在伤害别人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now who's doing the hurting?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.22,0:44:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不是大大，是你们在伤害，吼叫，或许杀戮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Not the grups. It's you hurting, yelling, maybe killing.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.68,0:44:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,就像你们记忆中害怕的大大一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Just like the grups you remember, and the creatures you're afraid of.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.72,0:44:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你们的行为和他们一样，你们最后也会变得和他们一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're acting like them, and you're gonna be just like them
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.19,0:44:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,除非你们让我帮你们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}unless you let me help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.23,0:44:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我是大大没错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm a grup...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.86,0:44:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,但我想帮你们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...and I want to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.99,0:44:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我恳求你们了，让我帮你们吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm begging you, let me help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.91,0:44:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,否则就什么都没有了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Or there won't be anything left at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.50,0:44:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托你们了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.92,0:45:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我们没时间等通讯器拿回来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We can't wait for those communicators any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.38,0:45:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我们一定要等着，这疫苗很可能是致命的 - 病毒是致命的没错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- We must. The vaccine could be fatal. - The disease certainly is.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.93,0:45:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我们还能活多久，几小时，几分钟？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How long do we have left? Hours? Minutes?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.97,0:45:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你到底还想等什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How much longer do you wanna wait?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.27,0:45:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,吵架一点意义都没有，我去看看舰长那边\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Bickering is pointless. I’ll check on the captain's progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.15,0:46:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Spock!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.84,0:46:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他死了吗，史波克先生？ - 还没有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Is he dead, Mr. Spock? - Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.35,0:46:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,还有三小时十一分钟，谢谢你，上尉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Three hours, 11 minutes left. Thank you, lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.65,0:46:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,把频道打开，准备好电脑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Keep this channel open. Clear your computers.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.82,0:47:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,- 麦考伊怎么了？ - 他自己注射了疫苗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- What happened to McCoy? - He injected himself with the vaccine.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.66,0:47:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我发现他的时候已经昏迷不醒了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He was unconscious when I found him.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.88,0:47:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你看他的脸\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Look at his face.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.17,0:47:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,蓝斑在消褪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The blemishes are fading.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.18,0:47:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They're fading.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.38,0:47:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,医生的想法真心不懂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I never will understand the medical mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.85,0:48:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,这是不是件好事，米莉？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Is this supposed to be a good thing, Miri?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.94,0:48:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,当然是啦\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Of course it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.95,0:48:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,他们还只是一群孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They were just children.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.20,0:48:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,- 把他们留给医疗队… - “还是孩子”\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- To leave them with a medical team-- - Just children.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.08,0:48:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,他们都要三百多岁了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Three hundred years old and more.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.21,0:48:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经联络了太空总部，他们已经派去了老师和顾问\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've already contacted Space Central. They'll send teachers, advisers.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.13,0:48:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我猜还要带上训导员吧 - 他们会没事的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- And truant officers, I presume. - They'll be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.13,0:48:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,米莉，她真的很爱你，你知道吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Miri... She really loved you, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.43,0:48:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.27,0:48:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我从来不和比我年纪大的女人恋爱，文书小姐\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I never get involved with older women, yeoman.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.82,0:48:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- 史波克先生？ - 什么吩咐，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Mr. Spock? - Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.53,0:49:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,- 全速前进，一级曲速 - 是，舰长，一级曲速\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Full ahead, warp factor 1. - Warp factor 1, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.44,0:49:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,本集结束
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.28,0:49:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢观赏
